{"id":511296,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":7,"day":11}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"庆祝中国共产党诞生五十周年,向着太阳唱颂歌","genre":"","count":"207","ytitle":"","mtitle":"钢花艳艳开万代","ftitle":"","authors":["周仁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七○二九厂工人　周仁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢工，情满怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑迎节日战炉台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千座炉门咱打开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地日月放异彩!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈旗帜映炉膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中南海电光亮心坎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆道路鼓虎劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁山钢海听调派!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左挥钢钎蛟龙腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯生产力论黑货化尘埃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右舞钢钎彩霞飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢梁、钢柱奔四海……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千种钢，万种材，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤将祖国巧打扮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想照钢城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢花艳艳开万代!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢工，情满怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死为党挑重担——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热汗催动钢水涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出一个新时代!"}]}